data.name: Medic-care
data.description: The Medic Care website theme is designed specifically for health specialists and is built on the Bootstrap 5 CSS layout. Its clean and professional appearance make it an ideal choice for creating a web presence. The theme includes a timeline feature with left and right items that can be easily customized using Font Awesome icons. It also includes a booking form for appointments that can be easily integrated with a PHP script.

data.name: Global
